            <p>A fully-funded accelerator for all-female, all-technical founding teams.
              Two weeks living and building together in Norway, followed by a six-week hybrid programme designed to take teams from zero to one, fast.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/about#past-events" class="card">
            <h3>events</h3>
            <p>Hackathons, workshops, and build days for technical women who want to start companies.
              These are hands-on by design: learn how to ship, meet potential co-founders, and figure out whether founding is for you.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/apply/join-community" class="card">
            <h3>community</h3>
            <p>A growing, high-signal network of technical women at different stages of the founder journey.
              We design environments where co-founder relationships form naturally, not through forced matching.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
